sequenceDiagram
    participant Test as Test Framework<br/>(Go)
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant TrainOp as Training Operator
    participant KubeRay as KubeRay Operator
    participant Kueue as Kueue Controller
    participant Master as Master Pod<br/>(Training CUDA/ROCm)
    participant Worker as Worker Pods<br/>(Training CUDA/ROCm)
    participant RayHead as Ray Head Pod<br/>6379, 8265, 10001/TCP
    participant RayWorker as Ray Worker Pods
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant HF as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Prom as Prometheus<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Test, Prom: Flow 1: PyTorchJob Model Fine-Tuning (KFTO)
    Test->>K8sAPI: Create PyTorchJob CR<br/>HTTPS/6443, Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>TrainOp: Watch event<br/>ServiceAccount
    TrainOp->>K8sAPI: Create Master + Worker Pods<br/>ServiceAccount
    K8sAPI-->>Master: Schedule Pod
    K8sAPI-->>Worker: Schedule Pod(s)
    Master->>Worker: NCCL collective comms<br/>TCP, plaintext
    Worker-->>Master: Gradient sync
    Master->>K8sAPI: Write to PVC (model output)
    Test->>Prom: Query GPU utilization<br/>HTTPS/443, Bearer Token
    Prom-->>Test: Metrics response

    Note over Test, Prom: Flow 2: Ray Cluster MNIST Training (ODH)
    Test->>K8sAPI: Create Notebook CR<br/>HTTPS/6443, Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>KubeRay: Watch RayCluster CR<br/>ServiceAccount
    Test->>K8sAPI: Create ClusterQueue + LocalQueue<br/>HTTPS/6443
    K8sAPI->>Kueue: Watch Workload admission<br/>ServiceAccount
    Kueue-->>K8sAPI: Admit workload
    KubeRay->>K8sAPI: Create Ray Head + Worker Pods<br/>ServiceAccount
    K8sAPI-->>RayHead: Schedule Pod
    K8sAPI-->>RayWorker: Schedule Pod(s)
    RayHead->>RayWorker: Task distribution<br/>Redis/6379, gRPC/10001, plaintext
    RayWorker-->>RayHead: Results
    Test->>RayHead: Submit job via Dashboard<br/>HTTPS/443 (Route), Bearer Token

    Note over Test, Prom: Flow 3: FMS SFT Training with Kueue Quota
    Test->>S3: Download model artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443, Access Key
    S3-->>Test: Model data
    Test->>K8sAPI: Create ClusterQueue + LocalQueue + ResourceFlavor<br/>HTTPS/6443
    K8sAPI->>Kueue: Watch resources<br/>ServiceAccount
    Test->>K8sAPI: Create PyTorchJob with Kueue labels<br/>HTTPS/6443
    Kueue->>K8sAPI: Admit/suspend workload<br/>ServiceAccount
    K8sAPI->>TrainOp: Watch PyTorchJob<br/>ServiceAccount
    TrainOp->>K8sAPI: Create fms-hf-tuning Pods
    K8sAPI-->>Master: Schedule Pod (fms-hf-tuning)
    Master->>K8sAPI: Read model from PVC
    Master->>K8sAPI: Write fine-tuned model to PVC
    Test->>S3: Upload fine-tuned model<br/>HTTPS/443, Access Key
